"title": "4468: horticulture",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4468",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The art of garden cultivation, first practised in the Garden of Eden.</p>\n<h2>Horticulture in the Garden of Eden</h2>\n<h3>The man and woman tended the garden</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:15-Gen2:23\">GEN 2:15–2:23</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The fall brought about a change in human priorities from horticulture to agriculture</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17-Gen3:19\">GEN 3:17–3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:2\">GEN 4:2</a></p>\n<h2>Egyptian agriculture is likened to horticulture</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:10-Deut11:11\">DEU 11:10–11:11</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Horticulture is totally dependent on good irrigation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:11\">ISA 58:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:4-Gen2:14\">GEN 2:4–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:10\">GEN 13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:5-Num24:7\">NUM 24:5–24:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:16\">JOB 8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:12\">SNG 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:15\">SNG 4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:3\">ISA 51:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:12\">JER 31:12</a></p>\n<h2>Those who practised horticulture</h2>\n<h3>Kings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:5-Eccl2:6\">ECC 2:5–2:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:2\">1KI 21:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:18\">2KI 21:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:26\">2KI 21:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:4\">2KI 25:4</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:4\">JER 39:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:7\">JER 52:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:15\">NEH 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:5-Esth1:6\">EST 1:5–1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:7-Esth7:8\">EST 7:7–7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song8:13\">SNG 8:13</a></p>\n<h3>Common people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:28\">JER 29:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:1-Jer29:7\">JER 29:1–29:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:41\">JHN 19:41</a></p>\n<h3>Gardeners</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:15\">JHN 20:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:7\">ISA 5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:1\">JHN 15:1</a></p>\n<h2>Kinds of horticulture</h2>\n<h3>Vegetable gardens</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:2\">1KI 21:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Fruit gardens</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:14\">AMO 9:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:16-Gen2:17\">GEN 2:16–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:3\">GEN 3:1–3:3</a></p>\n<h3>Herb gardens</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:42\">LUK 11:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song6:2\">SNG 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:31-Matt13:32\">MAT 13:31–13:32</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:31-Mark4:32\">MRK 4:31–4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:19\">LUK 13:19</a></p>\n<h2>Horticultural diseases and pestilence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:9\">AMO 4:9</a></strong></p>",
